ts. Returns false for agents that run\\n// hooks as subprocesses but can't relay user input.\\nCanRespondToPrompts() bool\\n```\\n\\nOr alternatively, a simpler approach: have each agent declare its env var in the registry, and `hasTTY()` iterates the list. That way adding a new agent with a non-interactive env var is just a registration, not a code change in the strategy layer.\\n\\nBut for now this hardcoded check matches the existing pattern (Gemini, Factory AI) and ships the fix. Want me to commit this, or do you want to think about the interface approach first?\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":1,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":276,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":105564,\"output_tokens\":286,\"server_tool_use\":{\"web_search_requests\":0,\"web_fetch_requests\":0},\"service_tier\":\"standard\",\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":276,\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0},\"inference_geo\":\"\",\"iterations\":[],\"speed\":\"standard\"}},\"requestId\":\"req_011CYhaNaaWH5X9wrmX1h5ob\",\"type\":\"assistant\",\"uuid\":\"0cf77db2-e894-4ef1-a778-112eda47dcd6\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-04T06:35:44.864Z\"}\n{\"parentUuid\":\"0cf77db2-e894-4ef1-a778-112eda47dcd6\",\"isSidechain\":false,\"userType\":\"external\",\"cwd\":\"/Users/alex/workspace/cli/.worktrees/5\",\"sessionId\":\"e73fdc2e-be24-417b-a111-12fff5857e65\",\"version\":\"2.1.63\",\"gitBranch\":\"alex/add-copilot-agent\",\"slug\":\"shiny-herding-gosling\",\"type\":\"progress\",\"data\":{\"type\":\"hook_progress\",\"hookEvent\":\"Stop\",\"hookName\":\"Stop\",\"command\":\"go run ${CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR}/cmd/entire/main.go hooks claude-code stop\"},\"parentToolUseID\":\"9ce282f9-f66e-460d-b5de-a61431779090\",\"toolUseID\":\"9ce282f9-f66e-460d-b5de-a61431779090\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-04T06:35:44.898Z\",\"uuid\":\"0d03e38b-90ad-4f01-9f4c-5eb8e05dcf4a\"}\n{\"parentUuid\":\"0d03e38b-90ad-4f01-9f4c-5eb8e05dcf4a\",\"isSidechain\":false,\"userType\":\"external\",\"cwd\":\